{
  "texts": [
    "In all plots, vPIM represents the implementation of our prototype with all optimizations enabled (C Code Enhancement, Prefetch Cache, Request Batching, and Parallel Handling).",
    "In Section 5.2 and Section 5.3.1, we evaluate the performance of vPIM compared to native.",
    "In Section 5.4, we evaluate the effectiveness of each optimization.",
    "The native is run in performance mode.",
    "Each result is a mean of five runs.Metrics."
  ]
}